model.npc

Interface NPC

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Brother, EnemyTrainer, Gentleman, Merchant, OldLady, ProfessorOak, RegularMan, SafariAgent, Sister, Woman

    public interface NPC
    This class represents an NPC object. Most NPCs are interaction-limited, meaning they only hold brief conversations. A few NPCs can initiate a Trainer battle.
    Author:
    Alan D., Paria K., Samantha F., Rajeev R., Scrum Master: Niven Francis, CSC 335 Final Project
